284
00:09:49.089 --> 00:09:50.590
Hope she's. uh.
f‐feeling better.

285
00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:51.883
Oh. thank you. that's ‐‐
that's very thoughtful.

286
00:09:51.883 --> 00:09:52.884
Yeah. she's doing great.

287
00:09:52.884 --> 00:09:54.552
Oh. uh. I brought that. uh.

288
00:09:54.552 --> 00:09:55.970
