289
00:09:55.970 --> 00:09:57.180
Right. thank you very much
for that.

290
00:09:57.180 --> 00:09:58.306
This is Marcus.

291
00:09:58.306 --> 00:09:59.724
He's. uh.
Fred's neighbor.

292
00:09:59.724 --> 00:10:00.767
