303
00:10:19.119 --> 00:10:21.287
Uh. well. I'm afraid
there's not much I can tell you.

304
00:10:21.287 --> 00:10:22.455
Of course. Right.

305
00:10:22.455 --> 00:10:24.249
Did you notice anything
out of the ordinary

306
00:10:24.249 --> 00:10:25.458
