328
00:11:03.913 --> 00:11:05.415
Um...

329
00:11:05.415 --> 00:11:09.460
♪♪

330
00:11:09.460 --> 00:11:11.796
That guy's after
my girlfriend.
Mm. Yeah.

331
00:11:11.796 --> 00:11:12.797
Fun.

332
00:11:12.797 --> 00:11:14.090
Okay. I'm gonna start

333
00:11:14.090 --> 00:11:15.884
