362
00:12:21.908 --> 00:12:25.370
I know.
and I'm pissed about it.

363
00:12:25.370 --> 00:12:27.121
But he's my wife's
favorite cousin.

364
00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:29.207
which means
he's my favorite cousin.

365
00:12:29.207 --> 00:12:31.376
so prison's not an option.

366
00:12:31.376 --> 00:12:35.046
